===================
*     README      *
===================

1. Install

    a. Requirements:
      - i686, ppc, SPARC, etc.
      - g++ >= 3.x
      - lttoolbox >= 3.1.0
      - libfoma0-dev >= 0.9.18~r248
      - foma-bin >= 0.9.18+r243
      - libxml2 >= 2.6.17
      - libpcre >= 6.4
      - libxslt >= 1.1.16
      - gnu make

    b. Building & installing
      $ ./autogen.sh
      $ make
      # make install

For build options, please see the INSTALL file.

